title: The first documentary about Czech community

description.body:
In 13 years, "lolko" has become an important part of life for many of us. Czech players, artists, content creators and fans have become an equally important part of the League of Legends world. We have created a Czech Mark that no one can erase.
Together, we're building unforgettable experiences. The first pentakill, a LAN party with friends, cheering in Svitavy, reaching a new rank or something completely different. You have also made history.
Let's remember together how important the Czech community is.
